1
00:01:49,776 --> 00:01:51,475
怎么了，妈妈？
 What's wrong, Mother?   Ruined.

2
00:01:51,865 --> 00:01:53,895
毁了！毁了！
Ruined!

3
00:01:54,135 --> 00:01:55,935
那个白痴把我们全都毁了！
That idiot has ruined us all!

4
00:01:56,005 --> 00:01:57,875
我们将不得不离开罗马！
We shall have to leave Rome!

5
00:01:57,935 --> 00:02:00,275
恺撒已经渡过了卢比肯河
Caesar has crossed the Rubicon.

6
00:02:00,335 --> 00:02:02,835
他带着兵马踏上了意大利的土地
He's on ltalian soil under arms.

7
00:02:02,905 --> 00:02:04,835
这可是叛国的行径
It's an act of gross treason.

8
00:02:04,905 --> 00:02:07,135
只带一个军团…如果你不介意的话
With a single legion, if you please.

9
00:02:07,205 --> 00:02:11,305
就不仅仅是叛国，而是自取灭亡的叛国之道
So not merely treason, but suicidal treason.

10
00:02:13,275 --> 00:02:15,835
打完了吗，主人？
Will that be all, Domina?

11
00:02:17,575 --> 00:02:21,274
  你听说了吗？   嗯，很奇怪
  Have you heard?   Mmm. Strange.

12
00:02:21,334 --> 00:02:23,104
做出如此蠢的一件事
Afoolishthingtodo.

13
00:02:23,174 --> 00:02:25,004
一个军团
One legion.

14
00:02:25,074 --> 00:02:27,834
我很想知道恺撒在想什么
I wonder what he's thinking.

15
00:02:27,904 --> 00:02:32,174
我不由得回想起当年我消灭那些伊利里亚人海盗的时候
I remember back when I destroyed the lllyrian pirates,

16
00:02:32,234 --> 00:02:35,004
其中有个很特别的经验老道的…
there was one particular old sea snake

17
00:02:35,074 --> 00:02:36,774
小型三层桨战船，如果我没记错的话
a Liburnian, if I recall.

18
00:02:36,834 --> 00:02:38,474
别说那些伊利里亚人海盗了
Never mind the lllyrian pirates.

19
00:02:38,534 --> 00:02:40,304
我们该怎么办？
What is to be done?

20
00:02:40,374 --> 00:02:42,204
我已经发布命令了
I have already given word.

21
00:02:42,274 --> 00:02:43,704
我的军团在集结
My legions are gathering.

22
00:02:43,774 --> 00:02:45,534
你会把恺撒他们给捻碎，对吧？
And you'll crush him, yeah?

23
00:02:45,604 --> 00:02:48,173
毫无疑问，那个可怜人死定了
Without question. The poor man is dead.

24
00:02:51,603 --> 00:02:53,873
你将带领尤比恩骑兵，侦察
You are to take our Ubian cavalry and scout

25
00:02:53,933 --> 00:02:56,803
由此到城市之间的路况以及防御的战略要点
all roads and defensive strongpoints between here and the city.

26
00:02:56,833 --> 00:02:58,383
向前推进直到遇到抵抗
Advance until resistance is met.

27
00:02:58,403 --> 00:03:00,103
如果遇到了公民
If and when civilians are encountered,

28
00:03:00,143 --> 00:03:02,553
就把我们的这份布告递交给他们
deliver the enclosed proclamation.

29
00:03:03,363 --> 00:03:06,633
如果没有遇到抵抗就直接把这份布告
If you encounter no resistance, go directly to the Forum

30
00:03:06,643 --> 00:03:09,893
钉到元老会论坛的门上
and nail it to the Senate door.

31
00:03:09,993 --> 00:03:10,793
长官
Sir.

32
00:03:10,813 --> 00:03:14,273
不允许进行烧杀掠夺
There will be no rapine, pillage or burning.

33
00:03:14,832 --> 00:03:18,472
  有问题吗？   没有，长官
  Any questions?   None, sir.

34
00:03:18,682 --> 00:03:20,182
执行命令吧
That will be all.

35
00:03:27,472 --> 00:03:30,272
你手下的这个乌瑞纳斯怎么这么闷？
What makes your man vorenus so morose?

36
00:03:30,342 --> 00:03:32,172
他只是对此有所抵触
He is stonewall Catonian.

37
00:03:32,242 --> 00:03:34,342
他认为我们犯了滔天大罪
He thinks we've committed a terrible crime,

38
00:03:34,402 --> 00:03:36,202
是逆天而行
a mighty sacrilege,

39
00:03:36,272 --> 00:03:38,272
应该被神严厉的惩罚
and shall be severely punished by the Gods.

40
00:03:38,342 --> 00:03:40,972
  他没准是对的   只有我们失败了才有罪
  He may be right.   It's a crime if we lose.

41
00:03:41,042 --> 00:03:42,971
而胜利者是无罪的
If we win, it isn't.

42
00:03:43,041 --> 00:03:45,771
我不过是在要求我的合法权利，安东尼
I am merely pursuing my legitimate rights, Antony.

43
00:03:45,841 --> 00:03:47,771
  当然   你认为我们可以信任他吗？
  Of course.   Do you think we can trust him?

44
00:03:47,841 --> 00:03:49,901
  谁？   卢西尔斯·乌瑞纳斯
  Who?   Lucius vorenus.

45
00:03:49,971 --> 00:03:53,601
噢，他是老13军团的人了
Oh. Deep 13th, him.

46
00:03:53,671 --> 00:03:56,501
鹰旗就是他奋不顾身找回来的
He'd follow the eagle up Pluto's ass.

47
00:04:15,340 --> 00:04:17,140
我跟你说过别来这里的
I told you not to come here.

48
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,740
我很想看看我的儿子
I had to see my son.

49
00:04:26,800 --> 00:04:29,200
你已经看到了，马上离开
You've seen him. Now go.

50
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:37,370
再也别回来了
And stay away.

51
00:04:39,679 --> 00:04:42,019
帮帮我，内奥比
Help me, Niobe.

52
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:43,469
我都快要疯狂了
I'm going insane.

53
00:04:43,549 --> 00:04:45,669
你不能就如此抛弃我
You can't forsake me.

54
00:04:45,752 --> 00:04:47,185
我可以的
I do.

55
00:04:47,469 --> 00:04:49,000
我不会放弃的
I won't give up. Don't think I will.

56
00:04:49,022 --> 00:04:51,786
你爱过我一次，就会再次爱上我的
You loved me once, you will love me again.

57
00:04:53,819 --> 00:04:54,559
我从来就没有爱上过你
I never loved you.

58
00:04:54,589 --> 00:04:56,909
你可以试着欺骗自己，但不要欺骗我
Lie to yourself if you want, but don't lie to me.

59
00:04:56,969 --> 00:04:58,789
离开吧
Stay away.

60
00:04:58,819 --> 00:05:01,029
你知道你将永远无法见到你的丈夫
You know you will never see your husband now,

61
00:05:01,069 --> 00:05:02,669
你知道的，对吗？
you know that, eh?

62
00:05:02,739 --> 00:05:04,769
他跟那些人都死定了
Him and all the rest of them are doomed.

63
00:05:04,839 --> 00:05:06,869
你别那么肯定
You don't know that.

64
00:05:06,939 --> 00:05:09,438
大家都知道会这样
Everybody knows that.

65
00:05:10,998 --> 00:05:13,098
或许会吧，但是我立过誓言（结婚时）
That may be, but I made a vow.

66
00:05:14,138 --> 00:05:15,598
离开
Go.

67
00:05:17,268 --> 00:05:18,898
离开
Go.

68
00:05:21,238 --> 00:05:23,898
我向冥神发誓，如果你不离开
I swear to Dis, if you don't go

69
00:05:28,068 --> 00:05:29,908
没什么事，他就走
It's all right. He's going.

70
00:05:29,968 --> 00:05:31,708
快离开吧
Just go.

71
00:05:34,308 --> 00:05:36,737
你答应过你不在见他
You promised you would never see him again.

72
00:05:36,767 --> 00:05:38,887
我没叫他来，我让他走
I didn't want him here. I told him to go.

73
00:05:38,907 --> 00:05:41,037
看起来可不像是这样
It didn't look like that.

74
00:05:44,567 --> 00:05:46,607
你可以跟爸爸说出真相，不是你的错
You could tell Papa the truth. It's not your fault.

75
00:05:46,667 --> 00:05:48,567
如果你跟我向他说…
If you and I spoke to him

76
00:05:48,697 --> 00:05:50,927
永远不要，你发过誓的
Never. You have sworn.

77
00:05:50,947 --> 00:05:53,617
你以为他战死了，爸爸会理解的
You thought he was dead. Papa will understand.

78
00:05:53,647 --> 00:05:55,777
他会把我们全杀了
He will kill us all.

79
00:06:08,306 --> 00:06:13,136
你常说你是花丛中的老手
You   you often say that you are adept with women.

80
00:06:13,206 --> 00:06:14,966
可不是闲谈时的自夸
No idle boast neither.

81
00:06:15,036 --> 00:06:18,266
从纳波到底比斯都有女孩子在晚上尖叫着我的名字
There are girls from Nabo to Thebes that scream my name by night.

82
00:06:18,296 --> 00:06:20,266
我不需要你的床上技巧
I have no need of your coital expertise.

83
00:06:20,286 --> 00:06:24,826
我问的是有关爱情的东西
My question more concerns their... affections.

84
00:06:24,876 --> 00:06:27,636
我可以在这方面给你一些指导
I'm your man for that to boot.

85
00:06:29,036 --> 00:06:33,005
我老婆，她…
My wife, she...

86
00:06:33,092 --> 00:06:35,560
你听到过她说，她恨我
You heard what she said, she hates me.

87
00:06:37,765 --> 00:06:38,825
你到底想问什么？
What's your question?

88
00:06:38,855 --> 00:06:41,195
非常明显，我如何能够让她不恨我？
How do I stop her from hating me, obviously?

89
00:06:41,225 --> 00:06:42,985
这可不是显而易见的问题
It's not obvious.

90
00:06:43,015 --> 00:06:45,005
我以为你特意的让她恨你呢
I thought you were making her hate you with a purpose.

91
00:06:45,035 --> 00:06:47,135
那根本不是我的目的，我为什么要那么做？
That was not my intent at all. Why would I do that?

92
00:06:47,205 --> 00:06:49,475
我怎么知道，你是个聪明人
I don't know. You're the clever one, you.

93
00:06:49,575 --> 00:06:51,475
你可能会有无数个理由这么作
There might have been 1,000 reasons.

94
00:06:52,055 --> 00:06:53,975
我爱她，希望她也爱我，
I love her, and I require

95
00:06:53,980 --> 00:06:56,314
而不是仅仅把我当成一个劳动力
that she love me also, else I am merely her slave.

96
00:06:56,395 --> 00:06:58,795
对此我无法容忍
I cannot tolerate that.

97
00:07:00,494 --> 00:07:01,594
那么，是什么让你关心她怎么看待你
Well, what care you what she feels for you

98
00:07:01,614 --> 00:07:03,524
如果我们在这一两个礼拜内就会死掉
if we're all going to die this week or next?

99
00:07:03,554 --> 00:07:07,004
我们很可能会死掉，但是我死后谁来祭奠我的名字
And so we are, but who will honor my name when I am gone?

100
00:07:07,114 --> 00:07:09,554
谁能为我向地狱女神跟冥王献上祭品？
Who will pay Proserpina and Pluto for my keep?

101
00:07:09,584 --> 00:07:12,074
谁会为我的墓碑撒上红酒？
Who will pour wine upon my grave?

102
00:07:12,614 --> 00:07:14,784
如果真的变成那样的话，我会做的
If it comes to that, I shall do the honors.

103
00:07:14,844 --> 00:07:17,044
这是最起码我可以做的
It's the least I could do.

104
00:07:17,234 --> 00:07:18,734
谢谢
Thank you.

105
00:07:20,094 --> 00:07:21,954
但是这不是一回事
But it's not the same thing.

106
00:07:21,984 --> 00:07:23,654
此外…
Besides...

107
00:07:23,714 --> 00:07:26,274
你也会一起死掉的
you'll be dead too.

108
00:07:33,043 --> 00:07:36,443
我在计划今晚的一个小聚会，我需要你…
I'm planning on having a small party this evening and I'll need you to

109
00:07:38,193 --> 00:07:41,023
你用香水了？
Are you wearing perfume?

110
00:07:41,123 --> 00:07:43,353
一点点而已
Just a dab.

111
00:07:43,443 --> 00:07:45,173
真是让人讨厌
It's horrid.

112
00:07:45,213 --> 00:07:47,533
马粪味更适合你
Horseshit suits you much better.

113
00:07:47,573 --> 00:07:50,043
现在我需要更多的人在外面守卫
Now I need you to get more men to stand guard outside

114
00:07:50,063 --> 00:07:52,213
当我的客人来得时候向他们问候
to greet my guests when they arrive.

115
00:07:52,213 --> 00:07:54,713
一个聚会？ 现在举行聚会是一个明智的举动吗？
A party? Is that wise, given how things are?

116
00:07:54,723 --> 00:07:57,212
香水的建议？ 还想有点什么建议？
Perfume, advice   whatever next?

117
00:07:57,392 --> 00:08:00,362
我只想说庞贝的手下正蠢蠢欲动
I'm just saying Pompey's mob is out for blood.

118
00:08:00,402 --> 00:08:02,422
  最好低调点   低调？
  It's best to lay low.   Lay low?

119
00:08:02,442 --> 00:08:05,162
我可不是一头蜥蜴，我永远不会被威胁
I'm not a lizard. I will not be intimidated.

120
00:08:05,192 --> 00:08:07,992
如你所愿，不过价格高点
As you like. Cost you extra though.

121
00:08:08,012 --> 00:08:11,012
你的报酬已经足够好了
You've been paid quite adequately already.

122
00:08:11,072 --> 00:08:13,512
更多的人手需要花费的更多
More men cost more.

123
00:08:15,652 --> 00:08:17,582
我会让卡斯特跟你谈的
I will tell Castor to speak with you.

124
00:08:17,612 --> 00:08:19,212
我并不是想要更多的钱
I don't want more money.

125
00:08:19,252 --> 00:08:21,232
那么，你想要什么呢？
Well, what do you want then?

126
00:08:22,702 --> 00:08:24,711
你知道我想要什么
You know what I want.

127
00:08:28,381 --> 00:08:29,451
就是像这样的…
Something like that.

128
00:08:29,501 --> 00:08:32,941
  你忘记你的地位了   我的地位是来自于我的家族的
  You forget your place.   My place is with my family.

129
00:08:32,971 --> 00:08:36,021
给个命令，我就会发动他们
Say the word, and I'll go to them.

130
00:08:40,901 --> 00:08:43,951
把你的事情做到我满意，然后…
Do your job to my satisfaction and...

131
00:08:45,551 --> 00:08:48,621
我想你是会得到适当的回报的
I'll see that you're properly rewarded.

132
00:08:52,401 --> 00:08:54,920
谢谢，主人
Thank you, Domina.

133
00:09:08,140 --> 00:09:09,790
庞贝的先锋
Pompey's outriders.

134
00:09:10,190 --> 00:09:12,580
他的军团应该也不远了
His legions won't be far behind.

135
00:09:12,690 --> 00:09:15,760
我们跟剩下的13军团的弟兄们在市集日就会被钉在十字架上
Us and the rest of the 13th will be on crosses by market day.

136
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:19,460
感谢神，我父亲没有活着看见他的儿子以叛国者的身份而死去
Thank the Gods my father didn't live to see his son die a traitor.

137
00:09:19,490 --> 00:09:21,339
最后现在就去死，嗯？ 走！
Best to die now then, eh? Go on.

138
00:09:21,379 --> 00:09:23,679
等等，我们不是来交锋的
Wait! We're not here to fight.

139
00:09:23,729 --> 00:09:25,649
“向前推进直到遇到抵抗”
"Advance until resistance is met."

140
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:27,639
这是我们的命令，也是我们所要做的
That is our orders. That is what we do.

141
00:09:27,699 --> 00:09:29,729
为什么不呢？ 弟兄们都准备好了，对吧
Why not? The boys are ready, aren't you, boys?

142
00:09:29,759 --> 00:09:32,109
让我们冲吧，来吧
Let's have a go. Come on!

143
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:34,019
不准交战！
No fight!

144
00:09:34,389 --> 00:09:38,479
不！不准交战！该死的白痴们！
No! No fight now! Damned idiot!

145
00:09:42,699 --> 00:09:44,149
列队防守
Form up and defend!

146
00:09:45,519 --> 00:09:47,639
记住你们受过的训练！
Remember your training!

147
00:09:47,909 --> 00:09:49,568
摆盾牌！
Shields!

148
00:09:55,028 --> 00:09:57,608
  坚守阵地   站稳了
  Hold your ground!   Stand tall!

149
00:09:59,608 --> 00:10:01,858
站稳了
Hold positions!

150
00:10:02,368 --> 00:10:03,698
回来，懦夫

151
00:10:10,698 --> 00:10:14,038
别动，懦夫，回来！
Stay in place, you cowards!

152
00:10:16,138 --> 00:10:20,747
恺撒的斥候已到罗马城30英里外
Caesar's scouts are only 30 miles from Rome.

153
00:10:20,777 --> 00:10:22,167
30英里？
30 miles?

154
00:10:22,187 --> 00:10:24,827
他的推进速度很惊人
His speed is uncanny.

155
00:10:24,907 --> 00:10:27,357
当然，他的人手不多
Of course, he has only a very few men,

156
00:10:27,387 --> 00:10:30,107
所以能够快速推进
which makes a fast pace easier.

157
00:10:30,347 --> 00:10:33,367
他领导的与其说是军队不如说是武装的暴徒
He is not leading an army so much as an armed gang.

158
00:10:33,387 --> 00:10:36,837
是非常无规矩，无道德的，甚至
It is all highly irregular, unethical even.

159
00:10:36,867 --> 00:10:39,697
现在甚至都不是战争的季节
Gods, it is not even the war season.

160
00:10:39,697 --> 00:10:42,857
他没有想要直接攻击罗马吧？
Surely he does not think to attack Rome directly?

161
00:10:42,887 --> 00:10:44,527
我认为这正是他所想要做的
I think that is exactly what he will do.

162
00:10:44,557 --> 00:10:46,246
他怎么能够期待成功呢？
How can he hope to succeed?

163
00:10:46,266 --> 00:10:48,196
目前的问题是
The problem is, at this moment,

164
00:10:48,226 --> 00:10:51,766
我们只有3个武装军团能够保卫这个城市
we have only three legions in arms for the defense of the city.

165
00:10:51,796 --> 00:10:53,836
当然，3个军团已经足够了
Surely, three is more than enough.

166
00:10:53,876 --> 00:10:55,826
通常的情况下是的，但是大部分战士
Normally that would be true, but most of the men

167
00:10:55,856 --> 00:10:58,766
都是新征召的，就像被斥候打散了的那些一样
are raw recruits like those who fled from the scouts.

168
00:10:58,796 --> 00:11:01,156
而剩下的都是打过高卢的老兵
The rest are veterans of Gaul.

169
00:11:01,216 --> 00:11:03,166
恺撒过去的手下不能信任
Caesar's men   not reliable.

170
00:11:03,196 --> 00:11:04,526
罗马不设防了！
Rome is undefended!

171
00:11:04,566 --> 00:11:09,186
我的军团正在尽快的集结
My legions are mustering as swiftly as possible,

172
00:11:09,216 --> 00:11:12,626
但是需要最少4天时间
but it will take at least four days

