511
00:34:53,815 --> 00:34:55,265
街上到处是尸体
The streets are full of corpses.

512
00:34:55,305 --> 00:34:57,935
任何人都有可能
It could have been anyone.

513
00:35:29,264 --> 00:35:32,294
“本诏告来自于盖乌斯·优利乌斯·恺撒
"These are the words of Gaius Julius Caesar,

514
00:35:32,324 --> 00:35:36,574
维纳斯的直系子孙，高卢总督
direct descendant of venus, Proconsul of Gaul,

515
00:35:36,574 --> 00:35:39,684
显赫的北方军团统帅
Glorious lmperato of the northern legions.

516
00:35:39,724 --> 00:35:41,853
公民们，我已经回到意大利
Citizens, I have returned to ltaly

517
00:35:41,893 --> 00:35:45,933
我的目的仅仅是为自己讨回合法的，道德的权利
with the sole intention of claiming my legal and moral rights.

518
00:35:45,963 --> 00:35:49,113
我并不渴求非法的权力
I have no desire for unlawful powers.

519
00:35:49,143 --> 00:35:50,933
我不会宣布任何人为敌
I will name no man an enemy

520
00:35:50,973 --> 00:35:53,433
既便他们这么做了
who does not so declare himself.

521
00:35:53,483 --> 00:35:57,533
经管如此，这些敌人的财产也不会被谋夺
Even so, the property of those enemies will not be appropriated

522
00:35:57,573 --> 00:35:59,773
他们的家人也不会被涉及
and their person will remain inviolate

523
00:35:59,803 --> 00:36:02,423
只要他们的反对能够是和平进行的
as long as their opposition be peaceful.

524
00:36:02,463 --> 00:36:05,463
此外，对于任何拿起武器反对我的人
Moreover, to any man that has taken arms against me

525
00:36:05,493 --> 00:36:09,792
只要现在感到后悔，我很乐于特赦他们
and now regrets it, I gladly offer total amnesty.

526
00:36:09,792 --> 00:36:11,982
但是，那些继续使用暴力
However, those that continue to use violence

527
00:36:12,032 --> 00:36:14,162
来反对我合法权利的人
to oppose my legal rights,

528
00:36:14,202 --> 00:36:17,322
他们会得到他们应受的惩罚
they shall receive that which they seek to give.

529
00:36:17,362 --> 00:36:20,152
在朱庇特主神的保护下
Under the auspices of Jupiter Capitolinus,

530
00:36:20,192 --> 00:36:24,202
这就是盖乌斯·优利乌斯·恺撒的诏告”
these are the words of Gaius Julius Caesar."

531
00:36:24,282 --> 00:36:25,022
你在干吗？
What are you doing?

532
00:36:25,072 --> 00:36:27,002
我已经完成了我的任务，而且我的罪孽已经够深厚了
I have done my duty and I have sinned enough.

533
00:36:27,052 --> 00:36:28,392
我离职
I resign.

534
00:36:29,092 --> 00:36:30,502
这是开小差
That's desertion.

535
00:36:31,182 --> 00:36:33,192
我已经是个叛国的造反者了
I am a traitor and a rebel,

536
00:36:33,282 --> 00:36:35,222
为什么不再加上个逃脱者的名字？
why not a deserter as well?

537
00:36:35,272 --> 00:36:37,341
你不能就这样离开13军团
You can't just leave the 13th.

538
00:36:44,711 --> 00:36:46,391
再见，波罗
Goodbye, Pullo.

539
00:36:53,211 --> 00:36:57,041
至维纳斯，生育的主宰者，我为您献上这份祭礼
To venus, the birth giver, I make this sacrifice.

540
00:36:57,771 --> 00:37:02,161
我是乌瑞纳斯氏族的卢西尔斯，斯特拉迪纳部落
I am Lucius of the vorenian clan, tribe of Stellatina,

541
00:37:02,221 --> 00:37:04,801
前任的13军团主力步兵团
formerly First Spear Centurion to the Prime Cohort

542
00:37:04,831 --> 00:37:07,160
矛兵百夫长
of the 13th Legion.

543
00:37:08,340 --> 00:37:10,750
我有一个妻子
I have a wife.

544
00:37:10,860 --> 00:37:13,310
她的名字叫内奥比
Her name is Niobe.

545
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:18,150
维纳斯，请让她像我爱她那样爱我
venus, let her love me as I love her.

546
00:37:24,120 --> 00:37:27,530
我奉献我的血，希望能够达到目的
I give my blood to make it so.

547
00:37:45,519 --> 00:37:48,319
对不起，我没有吓你的意思
Sorry, I didn't mean to scare you.

548
00:38:02,808 --> 00:38:04,888
你真漂亮
You're very beautiful.

549
00:38:07,218 --> 00:38:11,498
出于无知，我想看看我是否没有
I've come to see that it may be, through ignorance,

550
00:38:11,538 --> 00:38:13,348
像我应该的那样来对待你
that I have not treated you as I should.

551
00:38:13,378 --> 00:38:14,728
  像我应该的那样来对待你   请不要
  As I should treat you.   Please, don't.

552
00:38:14,768 --> 00:38:17,548
我们结婚的时候你还只有13岁
When we married you had only 13 summers,

553
00:38:17,568 --> 00:38:19,688
而且我很快的就离开了
and soon enough I was gone.

554
00:38:21,368 --> 00:38:24,818
但是你现在已经是个女人了，而我对女人一无所知
But now you are a woman, and I know nothing of women.

555
00:38:24,868 --> 00:38:26,828
我所知道的都是士兵的东西
Soldiering is all I know.

556
00:38:27,848 --> 00:38:29,947
很明显是没用的
Which is not useful.

557
00:38:31,687 --> 00:38:35,647
我曾经是如此的郁闷，冷淡跟不信任
I have been sullen and untrusting and cold.

558
00:38:36,757 --> 00:38:39,167
但是我不是石头做的
But I am not made of stone.

559
00:38:41,317 --> 00:38:43,517
我可以改
I can change.

560
00:38:43,577 --> 00:38:45,157
我可以用我女儿的儿子来发誓
I will swear on the life of my daughter's son.

561
00:38:45,207 --> 00:38:48,577
我会改的，如果你是这么希望的话
I will change, if you would have it so.

562
00:38:48,977 --> 00:38:50,567
请告诉我如果你不愿意的话
Please, speak if you would not have it so,

563
00:38:50,597 --> 00:38:52,867
我会离开并且不会恨你
and I will leave without rancor.

564
00:38:57,986 --> 00:39:01,666
  是我做错了事   怎么呢？
  It is I have done wrong.   How so?

565
00:39:04,996 --> 00:39:06,946
我是…
I am...

566
00:39:07,756 --> 00:39:10,416
我没有能够…
I have not been...

567
00:39:16,946 --> 00:39:18,966
过去的已经过去了
The past is gone.

568
00:39:19,066 --> 00:39:21,346
我们可以重新开始吗？
Can we start again?

569
00:41:21,579 --> 00:41:23,638
Ha!

570
00:41:52,190 --> 00:41:54,280
我不得不赞赏你
I applaud you.

571
00:41:54,680 --> 00:41:57,480
你就要像一个血淋淋的征服者一样进入罗马了
You're about to enter Rome as a bloodstained conqueror,

572
00:41:57,520 --> 00:42:00,470
但是你看起来就像一杯水那样平静
and yet you look as calm as a cup of water.

573
00:42:00,960 --> 00:42:03,660
我很高兴我看起来如此
I am glad I appear so.

574
00:42:15,410 --> 00:42:19,549
加咯斯，来点更高兴的音乐
Gracchus, something more cheerful.

